1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,720
00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

2
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,960
{\an8}Get rid of all the evidence.

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,800
{\an8}IN FATEH'S ROOM NOW

4
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:25,400
{\an8}Should I just kill you now?

5
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:32,600
{\an8}Without you,
it'll be easier for me to talk to her.

6
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:34,920
{\an8}Are you ready to die?

7
00:00:39,720 --> 00:00:41,200
{\an8}One.

8
00:00:45,040 --> 00:00:46,440
Two.

9
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:50,000
I place my trust in God.

10
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:00,680
I was just testing you.

11
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:22,719
{\an8}Datin Zizi wants to visit Fateh.

12
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:25,919
{\an8}Sorry, nobody is allowed to visit him

13
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:28,240
{\an8}without Mr. Thariq's permission.

14
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:32,879
{\an8}I'm akin to his mother. He needs me!

15
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:36,320
{\an8}I need orders and authorization
from Mr. Thariq.

16
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:39,399
How could you

17
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:44,800
separate Fateh
from the only mother he knows?

18
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,719
Be patient, Datin.

19
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:52,160
This is a hospital.

20
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,720
Don't make noise.

21
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:58,520
We don't want people to know
we'll make a scene here.

22
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,440
Okay, sir. We understand.

23
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,480
We'll be back later.

24
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,240
Datin.

25
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,639
Do you want to see Fateh?

26
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:15,079
Yes, please.

27
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:17,240
Of course. Come on.

28
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,360
Fateh!

29
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,759
Radwa.

30
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:40,880
Do you know that
Fateh is like a son to me?

31
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:45,359
I feel so sad to see him

32
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,160
unconscious like this.

33
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,200
I feel so helpless.

34
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:53,080
And Radwa.

35
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:56,960
She's been protecting
and taking good care of you.

36
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:03,160
Let's pray for him, Datin.

37
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:12,040
I believe Fateh will wake up.

38
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:15,840
He has to wake up.

39
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:21,119
- Radwa.
- Yes?

40
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:23,599
Can you give me
some time alone with Fateh?

41
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,599
Of course, Datin.

42
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:26,520
Thank you.

43
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:42,239
Fateh, take my secret to the grave.

44
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:45,040
When you're there, pray I'll go to heaven.

45
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,560
Datin, what are you doing?

46
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,759
I'm adjusting his pillow.

47
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:00,360
He looked uncomfortable.

48
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,839
What were you doing
with the pillow, Datin?

49
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:06,840
Like I said, I was trying
to make him comfortable!

50
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:20,999
Tell me what you were doing to Fateh!

51
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:23,879
I told you, right? I was just trying
to make him comfortable!

52
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:25,439
Is that wrong?

53
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:27,920
You were trying to kill Fateh,
weren't you?

54
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:31,480
How dare you accuse me like that?

55
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:36,080
I know what I saw!

56
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:40,279
If you try to do anything
to Fateh or try to hurt him,

57
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:43,640
trust me, you will not get away with it!

58
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,479
What's going on?

59
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:50,559
Datin Zizi tried to kill Fateh.

60
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:52,279
My goodness.

61
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:55,960
I wouldn't do such a thing.
Fateh is like my son!

62
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,720
I know what I saw.

63
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:02,519
You're ill, Radwa.
That's why you're hallucinating.

64
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,919
I'm not ill!

65
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:06,880
You are. That's why you slapped me!

66
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:09,800
Radwa.

67
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,079
Did you slap Datin?

68
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:16,920
She slapped me first.

69
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:19,679
You slap my wife?

70
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:22,400
She accused me of doing such nonsense.

71
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,440
It doesn't make sense!

72
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:28,839
She was trying to kill Fateh.

73
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:30,879
Ridz, you have to trust me.

74
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:34,319
No, Ridz. You have to trust me.

75
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:36,200
You've known me since you were a kid.

76
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:39,479
I would never do something like that!

77
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:41,160
You've got to trust me, Ridz.

78
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,360
You believe me, right?

79
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,680
Go home.

80
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:50,120
Go.

81
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:10,840
From now on,

82
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,720
I don't want anyone to visit Fateh.

83
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,720
Let's go.

84
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:25,399
I've known Datin Zizi since I was a child.

85
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,520
Datin Zizi is Mom's friend.

86
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:33,080
She was the most suitable patron
when Mom started Teduh.

87
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:36,399
She gave so much to Teduh.

88
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:39,879
Time, money, and energy. Everything.

89
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:42,320
And she took those kids as her own.

90
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,999
Your accusation is severe.

91
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:48,279
You're willing to say Datin Zizi
wants to kill the kids.

92
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:50,720
Where's the proof?
You don't have any, do you?

93
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:56,559
You have no idea how much it hurts me

94
00:06:56,560 --> 00:07:00,240
when the person I love and trust the most

95
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,120
doesn't believe me.

96
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,680
Radwa.

97
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,360
From now on,

98
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:12,479
you'll be with me all the time.

99
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:16,720
You'll eat, drink, sleep,
pray, and shower with me.

100
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,480
Understand me?

101
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,599
Please kill Fateh

102
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,159
before he gains consciousness.

103
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:34,360
When I tried to kill him,
there was a witness.

104
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:38,280
And please kill Radwa as well.

105
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:49,760
Don't touch Husniya Radwa.

106
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,760
If you do,

107
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,800
you'll die.

108
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:01,560
But you must help me.
You got me involved in this syndicate.

109
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:04,280
You were eager to become rich.

110
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,359
I have the market.

111
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,159
You have the product.

112
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:10,760
We do business and gain profit together.

113
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:14,559
Okay, for this business to be profitable,

114
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:16,039
you must help me.

115
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:19,120
If I get caught,
all of us will be done for.

116
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:25,599
Do you know why
I chose you to work for me?

117
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:31,039
Because I can supply the kids
and you can sell them?

118
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:33,400
There are plenty of suppliers out there.

119
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,840
But why you?

120
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:40,039
Because you handle Teduh.

121
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:44,240
Teduh belongs to Datin Tiana.

122
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:47,479
Thariq Ridzuwan's mom.

123
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,680
I don't understand. What do you mean?

124
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:53,879
It's time to execute our final plan.

125
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:56,160
Plan? What plan?

126
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:02,720
You were caught red-handed by Fateh

127
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,880
and Husniya.

128
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:07,239
That wasn't in my plan.

129
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,760
But I'm happy

130
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:11,720
because my plan has become more solid.

131
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,800
Yes, but what's the plan?

132
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:16,680
Don't kill Fateh.

133
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,640
Wait for him to gain consciousness.

134
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:23,960
Let him tell the police that you're
the leader of the Gajah Hitam syndicate.

135
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:27,279
Are you mad, Farez?

136
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:29,239
The police will look for you.

137
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,200
Obviously.

138
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:33,280
I want you to organize a press conference.

139
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:37,240
Call all the media and everyone.

140
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,720
At the press conference,

141
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:44,479
I want you to confess you're involved

142
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:47,639
in selling the homeless Teduh kids.

143
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:48,960
But

144
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:54,719
you must announce that
you're working with Datin Tiana.

145
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:57,199
The real leader
of the Gajah Hitam syndicate

146
00:09:57,200 --> 00:10:00,360
is Datin Tiana and her son,

147
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:03,400
Thariq Ridzuwan.

148
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:06,359
You want me to turn myself in?

149
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:08,639
No!

150
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:10,040
Just say

151
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:12,760
you'll provide all evidence

152
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:17,360
that shows Thariq is guilty...

153
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,880
to the police.

154
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:26,200
But what if I don't have evidence
that he's guilty?

155
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:30,960
It doesn't matter
whether Thariq is guilty.

156
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,640
Because society will punish him.

157
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:38,160
And the most important thing is

158
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:41,600
Husniya Radwa won't trust him anymore.

159
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:46,279
You're doing all this
for the sake of stealing

160
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,800
Radwa from Thariq?

161
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:52,160
Husniya will finally understand

162
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:57,679
that I've always been a good person.

163
00:10:57,680 --> 00:11:00,319
And I'm trying to save her

164
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:02,680
from the real bad guy.

165
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,759
Thariq Ridzuwan.

166
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,520
You're mad, Farez.

167
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:10,680
You're doing all this for a woman.

168
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:22,720
Yeah.

169
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:31,720
You want your family to die?

170
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,480
Do as I say.

171
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:10,120
<i>I didn't know you were a vlogger.</i>

172
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:13,079
Is there a problem with that?

173
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,000
Back then...

174
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,120
Do you remember

175
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,480
when you uploaded the videos

176
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:22,520
and someone commented on them?

177
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:25,120
He said he wanted to die.

178
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:28,879
And you made a special video for him
so he won't commit suicide.

179
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:29,840
Correct?

180
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:33,480
What are you trying to say?

181
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:35,920
You saved him.

182
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,680
He owes you his life.

183
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:43,080
Well, I couldn't have let him die.

184
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,080
Do you remember

185
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:52,280
saying you dreamed of marrying a commando?

186
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:55,040
He knows that.

187
00:12:55,560 --> 00:12:59,120
He joined the special forces to marry you.

188
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,040
No.

189
00:13:02,680 --> 00:13:04,200
No. Not me.

190
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:08,960
- Do I know that person?
- He'll introduce himself.

191
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:11,720
And he'll ask you to marry him.

192
00:13:13,040 --> 00:13:15,320
- Is he crazy?
- I know.

193
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:20,000
While we were training,
he knew I was dating you.

194
00:13:20,760 --> 00:13:22,920
Remember the guy who fought me
during the finals?

195
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:29,440
Ever since then,

196
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:32,640
he's been telling me
to break it off with you.

197
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,560
But I refused.

198
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:45,360
He called me.

199
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:49,200
He said he'd rescue me.

200
00:13:51,560 --> 00:13:53,200
But you said

201
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:56,800
you had me to protect you.

202
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:00,880
He was furious.

203
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,200
He tried to stab me.

204
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:11,200
And he was expelled.

205
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:15,519
But he called and threatened me
every day to leave you.

206
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:18,000
Otherwise, he would hurt you.

207
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:22,400
He stalked you every day.

208
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:27,960
Then, I went to see him.

209
00:14:30,280 --> 00:14:31,600
He was adamant.

210
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:35,000
He wouldn't let me be with you.

211
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:40,440
He threatened to kill you.

212
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:44,280
So neither of us can have you.

213
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:47,720
He told me

214
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:52,760
he'd rather see you die
than marry someone else.

215
00:14:55,160 --> 00:14:58,120
Is that why you said
you were engaged to Anita?

216
00:14:59,040 --> 00:15:01,880
I love you so much, Radwa.

217
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:05,160
I couldn't bear to leave you.

218
00:15:05,920 --> 00:15:09,200
My love for you is not as strong

219
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,920
as the fear of losing you.

220
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:16,920
I'd rather we break up

221
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:20,640
than have you die.

222
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:26,280
I could watch you from afar anyway.

223
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:32,640
Five years, darling.

224
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:38,680
I watched you from afar for five years.

225
00:15:40,040 --> 00:15:45,160
I saw you getting angry and sad.

226
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:48,280
I was mad at myself

227
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:51,919
because I couldn't take away your sadness.

228
00:15:51,920 --> 00:15:52,920
Why?

229
00:15:54,280 --> 00:15:56,080
Because I promised him.

230
00:15:56,800 --> 00:15:58,719
As long as I'm not near you,

231
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,520
he won't even try to.

232
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:05,280
But now?

233
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:06,880
He...

234
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:09,880
broke that promise.

235
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:14,560
He kidnapped you, Radwa.

236
00:17:22,560 --> 00:17:25,400
And you saved me

237
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:29,120
once again.

238
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:34,120
Hey!

239
00:19:49,360 --> 00:19:50,880
I thought I had killed him.

240
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:53,080
But apparently not.

241
00:19:54,760 --> 00:19:56,000
As people say,

242
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:58,800
bad people are hard to kill.

243
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:03,840
Now,

244
00:20:05,240 --> 00:20:06,280
he has come back

245
00:20:07,520 --> 00:20:09,040
to steal you away from me.

246
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:15,440
He told Zafir to give you
the picture of Raudhah and me.

247
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:17,560
Because this is his plan.

248
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:19,560
To get us to divorce.

249
00:20:23,120 --> 00:20:23,960
And yeah...

250
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:28,480
I don't have proof
to tell you I'm innocent, darling.

251
00:20:29,360 --> 00:20:31,200
With only words,

252
00:20:32,120 --> 00:20:33,600
you won't believe me.

253
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:39,760
You said that

254
00:20:43,720 --> 00:20:46,560
I don't know what it feels like
when someone we love

255
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:50,439
and trust doesn't believe us.

256
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:53,080
Just so you know, darling, I do.

257
00:20:54,760 --> 00:20:57,119
I know what it feels like

258
00:20:57,120 --> 00:20:59,640
when the person we love and trust

259
00:21:00,720 --> 00:21:02,360
doesn't believe us.

260
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:08,720
I told you I didn't make Raudhah pregnant.

261
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:12,920
You didn't believe it.

262
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,839
You asked me for a divorce.

263
00:21:15,840 --> 00:21:17,200
Dear.

264
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:22,440
By the way,
the person who wants us to divorce

265
00:21:26,280 --> 00:21:27,840
is my old friend.

266
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:29,960
His name is Farez.

267
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,879
Stay here tonight, okay?

268
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:37,439
Someone will look after you.

269
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:39,200
Where are you going?

270
00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:45,360
I'm going to regain

271
00:21:47,520 --> 00:21:48,960
my treasure's trust.

272
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:18,640
Haider.

273
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:22,000
I'm in trouble,
but you're lying on this bed.

274
00:22:23,760 --> 00:22:25,440
I'm sorry.

275
00:22:27,120 --> 00:22:29,800
I'm truly sorry.

276
00:22:36,080 --> 00:22:37,120
Wake up, Haider.

277
00:22:39,920 --> 00:22:44,640
I promise I'll do
whatever you want if you wake up.

278
00:22:49,600 --> 00:22:51,080
Sing "<i>Dia Dok Kata</i>."

279
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:55,359
Did you just...

280
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:57,360
I woke up this morning.

281
00:22:58,280 --> 00:23:01,080
You said you're willing to do anything.

282
00:23:02,040 --> 00:23:03,640
Sing "<i>Dia Dok Kata</i>."

283
00:23:07,360 --> 00:23:08,319
Are you serious?

284
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:09,840
Yeah.

285
00:23:10,760 --> 00:23:13,080
You promised.

286
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:17,480
Dance as well.

287
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:31,600
People call me Demonio for a reason.

288
00:23:32,800 --> 00:23:33,720
Okay.

289
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:38,120
- Nobody's here.
- Over there.

290
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:39,840
No one's here.

291
00:23:59,800 --> 00:24:00,960
Louder.

292
00:24:12,800 --> 00:24:15,439
- Okay, enough.
- I'll slap you.

293
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:16,520
That's enough.

294
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:23,759
- You like that, huh?
- Yeah.

295
00:24:23,760 --> 00:24:25,000
I've recovered.

296
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:30,400
Thalia told me she scolded you.

297
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:36,320
If I could turn back time,

298
00:24:36,920 --> 00:24:38,480
I'd do the same thing.

299
00:24:39,120 --> 00:24:42,200
Even if it happened ten times,
I'd do it again.

300
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:45,400
Thankfully, Fateh is safe.

301
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:49,680
- We even managed to rescue other kids.
- Yeah.

302
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:54,679
This is our duty,

303
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:57,520
mandate, and responsibility.

304
00:24:58,240 --> 00:25:00,400
A little pain is normal.

305
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:02,399
Let it be purposeful.

306
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:04,360
As long as we don't sin.

307
00:25:08,600 --> 00:25:11,000
You've done me no wrong, Ridz.

308
00:25:12,120 --> 00:25:14,199
You don't have to apologize for anything.

309
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:18,000
But my heart will be more at peace
if you forgive me, Haider.

310
00:25:20,080 --> 00:25:22,320
I forgave you long ago, Ridz.

311
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:32,880
- Love you, brother.
- You too.

312
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:36,200
- Yeah.
- So?

313
00:25:36,800 --> 00:25:38,160
Did I miss anything?

314
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:40,840
A lot, actually.

315
00:25:41,800 --> 00:25:43,160
Farez.

316
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:45,200
- Farez?
- Farez.

317
00:25:45,720 --> 00:25:48,840
The guy who defeated you
at the tournament.

318
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:50,440
Farez.

319
00:25:51,280 --> 00:25:53,040
- He's still alive?
- Yeah.

320
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:58,800
Do you have a plan?

321
00:26:02,800 --> 00:26:05,280
You said you cared about me, right?

322
00:26:06,880 --> 00:26:08,920
I have another request.

323
00:26:15,560 --> 00:26:18,360
What have you done?

324
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,840
What's all this?

325
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,320
Come here.

326
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:28,760
Sit.

327
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:33,719
This is for all the pain you caused Radwa.

328
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:34,760
So please...

329
00:26:35,360 --> 00:26:38,799
Please don't die yet
because I haven't finished beating you up.

330
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:41,520
Okay? Did you hear me?

331
00:26:42,320 --> 00:26:43,440
Peace be upon you.

332
00:26:44,520 --> 00:26:47,400
We're from
the Conflict Prevention Department.

333
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:50,280
You're still alive!

334
00:26:52,320 --> 00:26:54,279
Calm down, Ridz.
You don't want him dead, right?

335
00:26:54,280 --> 00:26:59,079
I'm still not satisfied with this bastard.
Got it?

336
00:26:59,080 --> 00:27:01,240
Yes, I know, but you have to calm down.

337
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:20,759
You're pretty when you smile.

338
00:27:20,760 --> 00:27:22,039
But it's a pity.

339
00:27:22,040 --> 00:27:23,359
You look sad.

340
00:27:23,360 --> 00:27:25,839
I hate people in uniform.

341
00:27:25,840 --> 00:27:27,679
My dad was a soldier

342
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:29,759
who was willing to sacrifice
for the country.

343
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:31,439
But he's a failure as a father.

344
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:35,159
And a husband who's very good
at neglecting his wife.

345
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,839
Do you think I'm selfish?

346
00:27:36,840 --> 00:27:40,359
For hoping he's the one
who entered just now.

347
00:27:40,360 --> 00:27:42,959
No, you're not selfish at all, Radwa.

348
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:45,559
But he said he loves me.

349
00:27:45,560 --> 00:27:48,839
Do you mean
after he left you five years ago

350
00:27:48,840 --> 00:27:50,559
and got engaged to someone else?

351
00:27:50,560 --> 00:27:52,399
But he came back.

352
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:54,679
And? He made your sister pregnant.

353
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:57,399
Radwa, please open your eyes.

354
00:27:57,400 --> 00:28:00,119
There are a lot of soldiers
in this country.

355
00:28:00,120 --> 00:28:03,199
Commandos, police,
the Royal Malaysian Navy.

356
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:05,359
But you, Husniya Radwa,

357
00:28:05,360 --> 00:28:07,479
you only have your husband
to take care of you.

358
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:09,759
And he can't even fulfill
his responsibilities.

359
00:28:09,760 --> 00:28:13,199
What your husband did
isn't a regular mistake.

360
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:15,359
But it's the ultimate betrayal

361
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:18,799
of his wife,
who loves him with all her heart.

362
00:28:18,800 --> 00:28:20,839
Do you think my decision is right?

363
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:22,279
To divorce him.

364
00:28:22,280 --> 00:28:23,200
Yes.

365
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:25,400
As it should be.

366
00:28:46,840 --> 00:28:48,680
I swear

367
00:28:50,600 --> 00:28:53,079
I won't let you

368
00:28:53,080 --> 00:28:57,360
disrupt my life with Ridz anymore.

369
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:04,000
What's the matter, Datin?

370
00:29:06,040 --> 00:29:07,920
I don't want my family to die.

371
00:29:08,600 --> 00:29:10,639
But I don't want to go to jail.

372
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:12,840
What am I going to do now?

373
00:29:14,360 --> 00:29:15,720
We'll kill Fateh.

374
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:19,239
Leave the country.

375
00:29:19,240 --> 00:29:20,799
Escape to a faraway place.

376
00:29:20,800 --> 00:29:22,480
Start a new life.

377
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,400
What about my family?

378
00:29:26,800 --> 00:29:29,840
I understand you love your family.

379
00:29:30,680 --> 00:29:33,080
You've sacrificed a lot for them too.

380
00:29:33,840 --> 00:29:36,519
Now, let them sacrifice for you.

381
00:29:36,520 --> 00:29:40,279
Hey! They're my flesh and blood!
My family! My children!

382
00:29:40,280 --> 00:29:42,799
You won't survive in jail!

383
00:29:42,800 --> 00:29:44,279
You'll die.

384
00:29:44,280 --> 00:29:45,200
Right now,

385
00:29:46,280 --> 00:29:47,840
make a choice.

386
00:29:48,440 --> 00:29:50,360
Your family or yourself?

387
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:56,440
I understand this is
a very difficult decision for you.

388
00:29:57,280 --> 00:29:59,159
If you can't decide,

389
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,600
let me.

390
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:05,719
But after what happened to Radwa that day,

391
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:07,319
Thariq would tighten security.

392
00:30:07,320 --> 00:30:09,079
We won't get to see Fateh!

393
00:30:09,080 --> 00:30:11,639
I'll kill Fateh with my own hands.

394
00:30:11,640 --> 00:30:13,360
What about the police?

395
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:16,880
I'll just crash into them
with the kids inside.

396
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:20,399
The most important thing is that
Fateh has to die.

397
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:22,320
And your secret will be safe.

398
00:30:22,840 --> 00:30:24,639
What if you get caught?

399
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:27,000
I will never say anything.

400
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:30,199
What if you get shot to death?

401
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:31,720
Then so be it.

402
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:35,480
But I'll ensure that Fateh dies first.

403
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:38,360
You've sacrificed a lot for me, Datin.

404
00:30:40,600 --> 00:30:41,959
I'll be proud

405
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:44,520
if I die saving you.

406
00:30:49,360 --> 00:30:51,200
You caused problems for Thariq.

407
00:30:52,800 --> 00:30:55,040
So you are stupid. Got that?

408
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,920
Where did you get that photo from?

409
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:01,999
You're doing this,

410
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:03,959
gathering up your friends,

411
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:06,400
just for Husniya?

412
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:10,080
Where did you get that stupid photo?

413
00:31:11,560 --> 00:31:13,320
Why? Did you have a fight with her?

414
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:17,280
Where...

415
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:20,280
did you get that stupid photo?

416
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:23,360
She must've asked for a divorce, right?

417
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:26,400
I knew it.

418
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:29,920
Women who overthink like Husniya

419
00:31:30,840 --> 00:31:32,200
are easy to woo.

420
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:35,160
But destroying them

421
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:37,600
is easier.

422
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:40,759
Do you want to know why?

423
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:44,120
Because your wife is a madwoman.

424
00:31:44,720 --> 00:31:46,199
What did you say?

425
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:48,759
Your wife is a madwoman.

426
00:31:48,760 --> 00:31:50,120
Say that again.

427
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:54,240
- Your wife is a madwoman.
- My wife is not mad, bastard!

428
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:57,439
Do you want to die? Huh?

429
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:58,720
Demonio!

430
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:06,640
If I shoot this,

431
00:32:08,120 --> 00:32:09,759
you might not die.

432
00:32:09,760 --> 00:32:11,600
But you won't be able

433
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:14,120
to use it anymore.

434
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:15,920
Do you want that?

435
00:32:17,600 --> 00:32:18,920
So answer me.

436
00:32:19,720 --> 00:32:21,360
Where did you get that photo?

437
00:32:24,960 --> 00:32:26,600
Do you want it damaged?

438
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:29,239
I'll ask you one last time!

439
00:32:29,240 --> 00:32:31,640
Where did you get that photo?

440
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:34,440
I don't know. Someone gave it to me.

441
00:32:36,400 --> 00:32:37,240
Who?

442
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:44,720
Who gave it to you?

443
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:47,559
I don't know. All I know is that...

444
00:32:47,560 --> 00:32:49,399
It was already in my car.

445
00:32:49,400 --> 00:32:52,000
I swear I don't know.

446
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:12,600
All these women

447
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,560
look similar.

448
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:20,320
But they're not the same.

449
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:25,959
I want her to have
the same height as Husniya Radwa!

450
00:33:25,960 --> 00:33:27,839
The bone structure,

451
00:33:27,840 --> 00:33:30,600
size, and everything
must be the same! Understood?

452
00:33:32,360 --> 00:33:33,839
Okay, boss.

453
00:33:33,840 --> 00:33:36,280
We'll find out more later.

454
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,440
Why are you nervous?

455
00:33:39,280 --> 00:33:40,640
No, boss.

456
00:33:41,240 --> 00:33:42,280
Our men

457
00:33:43,320 --> 00:33:44,840
didn't get to kill Zafir.

458
00:33:45,560 --> 00:33:47,120
The Holy Dragon saved him.

459
00:33:50,520 --> 00:33:53,840
Didn't you tell us to find and kill him?

460
00:33:54,640 --> 00:33:57,479
Let it be. He knows nothing.

461
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:59,320
No point in Thariq having him.

462
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:04,120
So why were you so eager
to kill him that day, boss?

463
00:34:05,040 --> 00:34:06,120
Just for the sake of it.

464
00:34:09,600 --> 00:34:11,400
Because I hate seeing his face.

465
00:34:13,679 --> 00:34:15,280
Because he likes Husniya.

466
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:18,239
He deserves to die anyway.

467
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:22,800
Anyway, I have a task for him.

468
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:25,400
What is it, boss?

469
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:29,560
To distract Thariq and the Holy Dragon.

470
00:34:31,080 --> 00:34:32,760
They'll focus on Zafir.

471
00:34:33,320 --> 00:34:36,520
My plan for Zizi will proceed
without interruption.

472
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:43,760
You are an intelligent mastermind, boss.

473
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:45,560
A genius.

474
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:49,199
To qualify as Husniya Radwa's lover,

475
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:52,840
the greatest woman in the world,

476
00:34:53,639 --> 00:34:55,159
you have to be smart.

477
00:34:56,400 --> 00:34:58,560
Well done, boss. Well done.

478
00:35:00,360 --> 00:35:01,200
All right.

479
00:35:01,720 --> 00:35:02,560
Leave.

480
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:09,359
Go to sleep. You're exhausted.

481
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:11,519
Farez is planning something right now.

482
00:35:11,520 --> 00:35:15,840
With each second I sleep, I'm giving him
a chance to expedite his plan.

483
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:18,719
So you want to keep beating up Zafir?

484
00:35:18,720 --> 00:35:21,320
Farez has been planning this for years.

485
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:24,600
He won't be stupid enough
to show his face to Zafir.

486
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:27,640
Someone else must've been
meeting him all this time.

487
00:35:29,080 --> 00:35:33,279
I've asked our team to check
all footage from Zafir's housing area

488
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:36,439
and from the hotel
where you met your sister-in-law that day.

489
00:35:36,440 --> 00:35:38,840
There must be a loophole somewhere.

490
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:45,480
What are you thinking?

491
00:35:48,520 --> 00:35:51,200
We all know that Chi Beng

492
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:54,560
and Zahid worked with Gajah Hitam.

493
00:35:56,560 --> 00:36:00,000
And Farez used them to distract you.

494
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:06,040
So that he can see Radwa.

495
00:36:08,520 --> 00:36:12,520
So that means Farez
is the head of Gajah Hitam?

496
00:36:15,520 --> 00:36:16,360
Chi Beng.

497
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:19,599
Chi Beng and Zahid are dead, right?

498
00:36:19,600 --> 00:36:21,600
But Farez seems relaxed.

499
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:24,479
So that means

500
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:27,040
someone else is carrying out his plan.

501
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:31,199
But it's not Zafir.

502
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:33,200
We must find out who it is.

503
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:40,040
Datin.

504
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:47,559
Why do you want to see me?

505
00:36:47,560 --> 00:36:49,360
I just want to say I'm sorry.

506
00:36:50,240 --> 00:36:51,600
On behalf of Radwa.

507
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:56,280
She shouldn't have accused you like that.

508
00:36:58,120 --> 00:37:00,719
And I'm sorry for what Radwa did to you.

509
00:37:00,720 --> 00:37:02,439
She slapped you.

510
00:37:02,440 --> 00:37:03,360
And I hope...

511
00:37:04,200 --> 00:37:06,080
I hope you can forgive her.

512
00:37:09,640 --> 00:37:10,960
Do you want to see Fateh?

513
00:37:12,640 --> 00:37:13,759
Okay.

514
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:15,919
I forgive Radwa.

515
00:37:15,920 --> 00:37:18,519
And thank you for believing in me.

516
00:37:18,520 --> 00:37:21,479
All right, I'll handle something first.

517
00:37:21,480 --> 00:37:22,840
Sure.

518
00:37:23,600 --> 00:37:24,440
Okay.

519
00:37:34,560 --> 00:37:36,040
Change of plans.

520
00:37:36,600 --> 00:37:38,319
Thariq allowed me to see Fateh.

521
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:40,120
I'll kill him.

522
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:52,799
You may enter, Datin.

523
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:54,320
Just you.

524
00:37:55,560 --> 00:37:56,560
Okay.

525
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:15,560
I knew it.

526
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:19,559
I knew Radwa wasn't lying.

527
00:38:19,560 --> 00:38:22,680
And now I have proof
of you attempting to kill Fateh.

528
00:38:24,320 --> 00:38:25,959
I'm sorry, Ridz.

529
00:38:25,960 --> 00:38:27,480
Please let me go.

530
00:38:31,720 --> 00:38:33,040
But why?

531
00:38:33,680 --> 00:38:35,200
Why do you want to kill Fateh?

532
00:38:36,600 --> 00:38:40,879
Because you sold my friends

533
00:38:40,880 --> 00:38:42,400
at Teduh.

534
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:47,319
Ridz, I swear I won't do it again.

535
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:48,919
Please let me go.

536
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:50,519
I'm sorry, Ridz.

537
00:38:50,520 --> 00:38:52,479
Please. I don't want to go to jail.

538
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:55,280
Please, let me go.

539
00:38:57,400 --> 00:39:01,480
Since you're a friend of my mom

540
00:39:02,200 --> 00:39:04,400
and I have so much respect for you,

541
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:06,640
I'll let you go.

542
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:27,640
Fateh is fine.

543
00:39:28,600 --> 00:39:30,359
He's gained consciousness.

544
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:31,800
Thank goodness.

545
00:39:34,080 --> 00:39:36,920
Darling, I want you to understand this.

546
00:39:38,360 --> 00:39:42,560
We need proof to take action
for such accusations, okay?

547
00:39:43,640 --> 00:39:45,399
I understand, dear.

548
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:47,520
I was just being emotional.

549
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:50,040
- I'm sorry.
- It's okay.

550
00:39:52,920 --> 00:39:55,360
So what will happen to Datin Zizi?

551
00:39:56,440 --> 00:39:58,160
Don't think about that.

552
00:39:58,840 --> 00:40:00,280
Let me settle it, okay?

553
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:15,480
Why are you looking at me like that?

554
00:40:17,120 --> 00:40:18,360
Do you miss me?

555
00:40:25,160 --> 00:40:27,640
When you told me about Datin Zizi,

556
00:40:30,200 --> 00:40:32,240
it's not that I didn't believe you.

557
00:40:35,480 --> 00:40:36,480
Darling.

558
00:40:41,160 --> 00:40:43,800
Even if the whole world didn't trust you,

559
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:46,640
I'd be with you.

560
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:50,440
And I'll always believe in you.

561
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:53,800
Thank you, dear.

562
00:40:57,840 --> 00:40:58,800
I...

563
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:02,760
I might be selfish sometimes, but...

564
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:08,119
But why can't you believe me
the way I believe you?

565
00:41:08,120 --> 00:41:12,479
No, dear. You're not selfish at all.
I'm the selfish one. I'm...

566
00:41:12,480 --> 00:41:14,599
I overthink that...

567
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:17,639
- No, you're not wrong. At all.
- If I'm not...

568
00:41:17,640 --> 00:41:19,400
If I'm not wrong,

569
00:41:23,200 --> 00:41:24,520
why would you ask for a divorce?

570
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:28,280
No, dear.

571
00:41:37,160 --> 00:41:38,000
No.

572
00:41:39,120 --> 00:41:41,560
I don't want to divorce you.

573
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:47,760
We'll never ever separate.

574
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:56,960
We'll be with our love, Thariq Ridzuwan.

575
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:03,160
Forever.

576
00:42:05,360 --> 00:42:09,360
{\an8}TO BE CONTINUED

577
00:42:16,920 --> 00:42:19,200
{\an8}Half of me. Half of you.

578
00:42:20,520 --> 00:42:24,399
{\an8}You look a bit like our future child.

579
00:42:24,400 --> 00:42:25,999
{\an8}I don't know why...

580
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:30,519
{\an8}<i>I don't know why I'm like this today.
I can't see or smell chicken rice.</i>

581
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:31,999
{\an8}I feel nauseous.

582
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:36,080
{\an8}NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW

583
00:42:37,600 --> 00:42:38,680
{\an8}Mom!

584
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:40,600
{\an8}Don't touch my wife.

585
00:42:41,320 --> 00:42:44,399
{\an8}Ridz. What are you doing here?

586
00:42:44,400 --> 00:42:48,119
{\an8}<i>I will announce that Thariq Ridzuwan</i>

587
00:42:48,120 --> 00:42:50,239
{\an8}is the leader
of the Gajah Hitam syndicate.

588
00:42:50,240 --> 00:42:53,399
{\an8}That's enough. Don't be upset.

589
00:42:53,400 --> 00:42:54,840
{\an8}Can I see you?

590
00:42:55,560 --> 00:42:57,120
{\an8}I want to vent again.

